{
  "stem": "27129.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But walking down the street, I heard a voice behind me, and she was calling me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My cousin was calling me, Abramic!",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I turn around, there she is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And it was right in front of her house, where she lived.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I went up there, and we were so happy to see each other.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And her brother already was there, you know.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we spent a couple of days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I didn't want to stay in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They said that the house, because she went there, they were, they were staying there in the ghetto in our apartment, my cousin.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In the ghetto, they were staying, three families, in the two rooms there were three families staying.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "An uncle of mine, the older brother of my father's, and, and they were the family.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where we lived, yeah, they made the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she told us that she went there, and the building is all in ruins.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Not-- the outside walls was still standing, but since people didn't have-- the Gentile people, the Polish people didn't have wood to, to heat up the houses in the wintertime, so when they took the people out and they sent them away to the concentration camps to, for, for, you know, to kill them, so they went in there.",
      "word_count": 59
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They tear up the floors and everything, and the, the, the the doors, everything they took out, and the window frames.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everything they took out, they broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I figure, why, why should I go there?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There's nothing for me to see, you know?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I stayed with my cousin a couple days and my future in-laws, and we decided to go back to the kids, you know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The kids were left alone in Liegnitz.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
